{"id":1811,"date":"2015-07-02T10:45:59","date_gmt":"2015-07-02T02:45:59","guid":{"rendered":"http://xbeta.info/?p=1811"},"modified":"2015-07-02T10:45:59","modified_gmt":"2015-07-02T02:45:59","slug":"tc-2015","status":"publish","link":"https://xbeta.info/tc-2015.htm","title":{"rendered":"关于Total Commander电子书及TC团购（2015）"},"content":{"rendered":"<h2>关于 Total Commander 电子书</h2>\n<p><strong>放弃实体书：</strong>编辑催了几年，我实在抽不出时间，就一直拖延。最终放弃实体书，在多名网友协助下，先发电子书。</p>\n<p><strong>百度阅读平台：</strong><a href=\"http://yuedu.baidu.com/ebook/1ec4abf0f46527d3240ce0ab\">《一本关于 Total Commander 的书》</a>，已经免费发布，适用 web、iOS、安卓。共15章 (20万字)，陆续更新中。</p>\n<p><strong>人民邮电出版社异步社区：</strong><a href=\"http://www.epubit.com.cn/book/details/4277\" target=\"_blank\">《Total Commander：万能文件管理器》</a> 免费在线阅读，免费下载 epub 和 mobi 电子书。</p>\n<p><strong>Word版：</strong>版本稍为旧一些，放在百度云可下载： <a href=\"http://pan.baidu.com/s/1mgEblX2\">http://pan.baidu.com/s/1mgEblX2</a> 密码: q5rt</p>\n<p><strong>其他平台：</strong><del>目前正在 yaniv 网友协助下，尝试用类似 github 的平台，markdown 格式，实现多人协作更新。如果顺利，将基于此更新，并转化为其他格式。（但这些更新无法同步到百度阅读平台）</del>没有精力，放弃了~</p>\n<h2>关于 Total Commander 团购</h2>\n<p>我没有精力，Ghisler 非常不积极，所以，可预期的未来不会有团购。</p>\n<p>大家不必纠结团购：没钱就点击123；等钱多了就全价购买。</p>\n<p class=\"book-title mb15\" title=\"一本关于 Total Commander 的书\">\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>关于 Total Commander 电子书 放弃实体书：编辑催了几年，我实在抽不出时间，就一直拖延。最终放弃 [&hellip;]</p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":["未分类"],"tags":["Total Commander","all"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/1811"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/users/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/comments?post=1811"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/1811/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/media?parent=1811"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/categories?post=1811"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/tags?post=1811"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https://api.w.org/{rel}","templated":true}]},"wp_type":"post"}